properties.name: hzero.service-init-registry.skip-expression
properties.description: 忽略服务spel表达式，以该表达式作为匹配规则，匹配成功的服务会被跳过初始化过程(eg."service.serviceName=='hzero-config'||service.serviceName=='hzero-oauth'").

properties.name: hzero.service-init-registry.health-check.connect-timeout
properties.description: 服务初始化注册中心的健康检查连接超时时间，单位ms.

properties.name: hzero.service-init-registry.health-check.read-timeout
properties.description: 服务初始化注册中心的健康检查读超时时间，单位ms.
